{"id": "1517724850628726884", "channel_id": "1505167541818101862", "type": 0, "author_id": "705407952575529022", "author_name": "water_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "# 取消300抽加三圍\n# Cancel 300 normal pull for stats\n\n# 要求新系統提供更高的三圍 (50% up) \n\n# Demand the new system grants stats boosted by over 50%.", "timestamp": "2026-06-20T02:56:42.354000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1505167541818101862", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.5.1.0 停服维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881"}
